rows.label: qev025302_MSG0001
rows.name: Ah! Yes yes. Hello hello. Welcome.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0002
rows.name: Did you bring a noka mirrorstone, perhaps?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0003
rows.name: If not, maybe hurry please, okay? Thank you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0004
rows.name: Ah! Yes yes. Hello hello. Welcome.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0005
rows.name: Did you bring a noka mirrorstone, perhaps?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0006
rows.name: Hmmm... Not very high quality, is it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0007
rows.name:
Though I suppose it's good enough to use on an
Earth-made Skell, maybe?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0008
rows.name:
Would you wait a moment? I'll refine repair materials
the likes of which you've only dreamed possible, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0009
rows.name: ...Done! Er, I hope this serves our purpose?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0010
rows.name:
You were surprised the refinement process was so
quick, yes? Surprised by the total superiority of
Ma-non technology?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0011
rows.name:
Of course you are. Our science is the finest in all
the universe, isn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0012
rows.name:
Not only will these refined materials repair your Skell,
they will also begin to bring its lacking defenses up to
a...reasonable standard?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0013
rows.name:
So, er, go on. Take them to the human waiting for
them at the test hangar, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0014
rows.name:
Not only will these refined materials repair your Skell,
they will also begin to bring its lacking defenses up to
a...reasonable standard?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0015
rows.name:
So so so please take them to the human waiting for
them at the test hangar, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0016
rows.name: My my my my. More business with me, yes?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0017
rows.name:
Unfortunately I have none with you, okay?
Sorry. So sorry. Bye now, yes?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0018
rows.name:
...A new deal? Hmm. I take it by your choice of words
you're offering some information or object of value in
return then?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_JNK0010
rows.name: Give Intelligence

rows.label: qev025302_SEL0011
rows.name: Offer to share Earth technology.

rows.label: qev025302_JNK0020
rows.name: Give Money

rows.label: qev025302_SEL0021
rows.name: Offer to pay Aganeba in credits.

rows.label: qev025302_JNK0030
rows.name: Barter

rows.label: qev025302_SEL0031
rows.name: Offer specialty products from Earth.

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0019
rows.name: Earth "technology"? Oh no. No no no.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0020
rows.name:
So it's like, um, when your people want to learn new
science, they don't go digging through ancient ruins,
right? No, of course not. No.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0021
rows.name:
I'm afraid there is simply nothing the Ma-non can learn
from humans, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0022
rows.name: Now, if you'll kindly...be on your way? Yes?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0023
rows.name:
The exchange of currency is the basis of commerce,
and seems the simplest method of purchasing
technology, does it not?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0024
rows.name:
However, we Ma-non live here on our ship free of
want or desire, don't we?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0025
rows.name:
We have little need to use your New LA money,
or to participate in your economy. You understand?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0026
rows.name: So, um, I'm afraid that's that's that's no deal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0027
rows.name:
Ah! I am interested in your specialty products, yes?
Veeeeery interested![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0028
rows.name: And what is it that that that you will be offering?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_JNK0040
rows.name: Furniture

rows.label: qev025302_SEL0041
rows.name: Promise Aganeba luxury furnishings fit for royalty.

rows.label: qev025302_JNK0050
rows.name: Toys

rows.label: qev025302_SEL0051
rows.name: Show your prized collection of mint-condition figurines.

rows.label: qev025302_JNK0060
rows.name: Food

rows.label: qev025302_SEL0061
rows.name: Offer Aganeba the first food that pops into your head.

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0029
rows.name: What is this you're offering? Junk, yes? It's junk? Yes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0030
rows.name:
I am unsure whether this feels desperate or simply
insulting. ...Er, that's not rude, is it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0031
rows.name: Anyway, um, no. Please be on your way, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0032
rows.name:
Oh! Oh my! These objects are most striking,
aren't they?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0033
rows.name:
Holo-figurines, they're called? For display in the home?
Yes, I see. Yes, very nice! Nice indeed![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0034
rows.name: But sadly my wife has forbidden me from such pursuits.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0035
rows.name:
I am something of a recovering addict, you see?
My collecting habit nearly drove us into debt.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0036
rows.name:
This makes part of me wither and die, but, uh, no?
Yes. I'm sorry, but it's a no.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0037
rows.name:
Kindly take your temptations and begone, okay?
...And remember to never take them out of the original
packaging![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0038
rows.name: Food, yes? Food?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0039
rows.name:
I will concede that in cuisine alone, Earth culture
shows remarkable promise, doesn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0040
rows.name:
But I see little reason to trade for it when I need only
walk into town to eat it, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0041
rows.name:
However, if you insist, I am willing to try a local
delicacy of New LA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0071
rows.name:
I previously heard from Matthew that this city once
stood in a place called America, yes?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0074
rows.name:
I would be willing to sample a local delicacy of
this...America. Something good, yes?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0075
rows.name:
It will need to be impressive indeed if you hope to
trade it for our technology, you understand?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0076
rows.name: Have you you brought your American delicacy?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0077
rows.name:
Then maybe hand me your personal recommendation
so I might sample it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0079
rows.name: So, um, what is this?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0080
rows.name:
A ham-burger? Interesting. I see a variety of
foodstuffs trapped between two grain-based discs.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0081
rows.name:
But, as they say, the taste will tell, right?
Er, they do say that, don't they? ...No?
Never mind.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0082
rows.name: *nom* *munch* *slurp*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0083
rows.name: ......[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0084
rows.name:
The taste is several orders less interesting than its
appearance, isn't it? I fear I am tongue-bored.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0085
rows.name:
I'm afraid I cannot offer our technology if you don't
provide food with more punch, can I now?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0086
rows.name: What is this we have here?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0087
rows.name:
A hot...dog? Surely not real dog meat, no? Ah. No.
It is simply meat in tubular form further encased in a
boat of carbohydrates, isn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0088
rows.name:
I will not deny it has a certain allure, no? And so easy
to carry about! But how does it taste?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0089
rows.name: *nom* *munch* *slurp*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0090
rows.name: ......[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0091
rows.name:
...HOT! AAAAUUUUGH! The tubular meat hides
burning juices, doesn't it?! Its oils assault my mouth![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0092
rows.name:
I think this hot dog is maybe a too-hot dog?
Clearly dangerous. Please take it back immediately.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0093
rows.name:
If you hope to trade for our technology, I must insist
you bring me a safer food, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0042
rows.name: Oh, what is this?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0043
rows.name:
Ah, so this is pizza? Mmm... Its chilled surface glistens
with frosty flavor, does it not?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0044
rows.name: Into my mouth with you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0045
rows.name:
*nom* *munch* *slurp* *chomp* *crunch*
...HRMMMR?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0046
rows.name: Th-this...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0047
rows.name:
THIS IS AMAZING, isn't it?! I think my mouth may be
alive for for for the first time?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0048
rows.name:
The gritty texture, yes?! The crunchy cheese, yes?!
The unyielding pepperoni, YES![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0049
rows.name: ...What's that? You're meant to heat it first?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0050
rows.name:
It doesn't matter! No! Nothing matters except pizza,
culinary crown jewel of all the cosmos![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0051
rows.name:
Even the Destroyer-King whose wrath rent planets in
twain would bow before the sheer force of this
deliciousness, would he not?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0052
rows.name:
I give thanks that that that I was born!
Thank you, Mother! Thank you, Father![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0053
rows.name: ...Hmm? Trade? Yes? What?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0054
rows.name:
OH! Yes! Our material refinement technique.
Next to this pizza, offering that old thing seems
tantamount to insult, doesn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0055
rows.name: Though note that will not stop me from doing so.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0056
rows.name:
You have a deal, friend! If you'll accept it, of course?
A silly little technological tidbit for a taste to quell a
Destroyer-King! Seems a little unfair almost, doesn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0057
rows.name: Er, you're certain, right? Then I have no objection.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0058
rows.name:
Ah, but teaching you the refinement method seems
inefficient, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0059
rows.name:
Why don't I simply perform it for you as a service from
now on?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0060
rows.name:
You'll still receive the results, so I assume you have no
further qualms?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_JNK0070
rows.name: Agree

rows.label: qev025302_SEL0071
rows.name: Accept Aganeba's terms.

rows.label: qev025302_JNK0080
rows.name: Refuse

rows.label: qev025302_SEL0081
rows.name: Object to Aganeba's terms.

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0061
rows.name: Your understanding is most appreciated, you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0062
rows.name:
From this point on, we Ma-non promise regular
deliveries of of of the materials you seek.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0063
rows.name: This is agreeable, yes?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0064
rows.name:
Hmm. I can understand your desire to to to refine
the materials yourselves, but...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0065
rows.name:
from an efficiency standpoint, I really must recommend
entrusting the Ma-non to handle production. Er, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0066
rows.name: Consider it a new chapter in our shared lives, perhaps?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0067
rows.name: Does that sound agreeable?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0068
rows.name:
Lovely! This has been a most successful negotiation,
hasn't it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0069
rows.name:
How fortunate are we to witness both of our cultures
take a grand step forward this day, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev025302_MSG0070
rows.name:
I look forward greatly to what else our partnership may
yield, okay? Okay![ST:wait ]
